tip.text: Spicy chkn hot pot rice is too sweet tho nice. Curry chkn nice esp if u like it with lotsa coconut milk. Bread that comes with curry is fantastic! Soft n tender! Must have!!
Beancurd with Almond Syrup - must have!!
Omega 3 Baby! is fantabulous!
Teriyaki Salmon - must try! Miso soup has salmon slices in it too! Yumz!
Lor mee gravy is too sweet for my liking. Quite a bit of ingredients tho.
Strawberry milkshake was ultra smooth!
Skipper's Delight Penne - The fish ws indeed uniquely delightful! Tenderness of the fish perfectly juxtaposed agst a lemon flavored crust....heavenly! Lobster bisque gravy tasted bitter twd the end.
Garlic Prawn Pasta! Don't leave Coffee Club without it!
Ice Earl Vanilla is a must try! The Bergamot makes all the difference!
Mushroom soup goes well with the biscuit tho would hv preferred it in a thicker consistency.
Duck Kway Chap is good!
